e of the seven DTUs and strict associations of independent DTUs with the host and environment in Colombia. The implications are discussed herein.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Guhl, Felipe", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ram\u00edrez, Juan David", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/1741124ec98bd142dbbea16fd543490b", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/0781bd786f6a8332b17d85353580b8b3a85b5507171a4ef1320d15ca211f4cd1", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/KCRE3G2M", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/KCRE3G2M", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/caa7652a0eb20cb1035be5f626fa6863!/b25989-28559", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"pages": "148-154", "title": "Infection, Genetics and Evolution", "volume": "20"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/1741124ec98bd142dbbea16fd543490b"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:KCRE3G2M"}, {"identifier": "10.1016/j.meegid.2013.08.028"}], "communities": [{"id": "biosyslit"}, {"id": "batlit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13472041"}}]}}, "title": "Retrospective molecular integrated epidem